assessment from out there.

35
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:25,230
Kinoto: Oh, no.
Please go on ahead.

36
00:01:25,290 --> 00:01:26,490
I’ll be right behind you, sir.

37
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,600
Rohan: Huh?

38
00:01:30,300 --> 00:01:34,500
( Kinoto grunting )

39
00:01:34,570 --> 00:01:36,670
Now, where is that room?

40
00:01:36,740 --> 00:01:38,370
I’d love to see it.

41
00:01:39,570 --> 00:01:40,810
( Kinoto chuckles )

42
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:44,250
( Metal clangs )

43
00:01:44,310 --> 00:01:47,280
Toyohiro: I didn’t think
my escape would go so smoothly.

44
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:48,780
Though I shouldn’t be surprised.

45
00:01:48,850 --> 00:01:52,390
