yoshikage Kira yet, have you?

46
00:01:52,450 --> 00:01:53,550
( Both growl )

47
00:01:53,620 --> 00:01:55,160
toyohiro:
Did it ever cross your mind

48
00:01:55,220 --> 00:01:56,460
