do it without a clean escape?

55
00:02:10,470 --> 00:02:13,370
See you, boys, and I definitely
wouldn’t wanna be you.

56
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:15,310
Josuke: Hey! Get back here!

57
00:02:15,380 --> 00:02:16,540
Mikitaka: No, Mr. Josuke!

58
00:02:16,610 --> 00:02:18,110
- Don’t come in here!
- ( Both gasp )

59
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:20,350
Mikitaka: I shall remain
in the tower for now.

60
00:02:20,420 --> 00:02:21,720
Josuke: Yeah, right!

61
00:02:21,780 --> 00:02:23,290
