Mikitaka: What? Why, josuke?

85
00:03:16,170 --> 00:03:17,100
Toyohiro: Piss off!

86
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:23,080
Josuke: Thanks to you
cutting this line,

87
00:03:23,140 --> 00:03:25,510
