josuke! Don’t you fall!

94
00:03:39,490 --> 00:03:40,530
Josuke: Yeah, as if.

95
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:42,260
Toyohiro: Props, friend.

96
00:03:42,330 --> 00:03:44,870
