you could have made.

99
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,410
I would have been
perfectly content

100
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:52,140
leaving this place behind.

101
00:03:52,210 --> 00:03:54,180
In fact, killing
you pigheaded boobs

102
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,140
never crossed my mind,

103
00:03:56,210 --> 00:03:58,610
but you just had to go
and force my hand!

104
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,250
so now,
for me to make my getaway,

105
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:02,580
