but to push you to your death!

106
00:04:02,650 --> 00:04:04,150
Josuke: Go to hell!

107
00:04:04,220 --> 00:04:06,120
Shining diamond: Dora!

108
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:09,660
( Yelling )

109
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:11,390
( Josuke gasps )

110
00:04:19,430 --> 00:04:21,170
( Gasping )

