- ( Mikitaka gasps )

144
00:05:42,420 --> 00:05:44,650
Okuyasu: Josuke, no!

145
00:05:46,250 --> 00:05:47,760
Toyohiro: Didn’t you
just say my attacks

146
00:05:47,820 --> 00:05:50,560
