They’re coming for you!

152
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:04,470
Shining diamond: Dora!

153
00:06:04,540 --> 00:06:06,370
Mikitaka: Mr. Josuke!
behind you!

154
00:06:11,850 --> 00:06:13,720
Mr. Josuke!

155
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:14,720
( Josuke groans )

156
00:06:14,780 --> 00:06:15,750
Toyohiro: Didn’t I tell you

157
