another onslaught.

165
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:35,400
Toyohiro: Now the time’s come
for the finishing blow!

166
00:06:35,470 --> 00:06:37,110
- I think i’ll aim for...
- Josuke: Hey, okuyasu,

167
00:06:37,170 --> 00:06:38,510
