to take you down.

177
00:06:59,190 --> 00:07:01,060
Toyohiro: What are you
blathering on about?

178
00:07:01,130 --> 00:07:02,600
Josuke: If i’m
remembering right,

179
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:04,270
you used the word "ricochet."

180
00:07:04,330 --> 00:07:06,270
yeah, that’s right.
You said your stand’s energy

181
00:07:06,330 --> 00:07:08,500
