like billiard balls.

182
00:07:08,570 --> 00:07:10,570
well, that is
what you said, isn’t it?

183
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:13,340
that’s right!
What are you gonna do about it?!

184
00:07:13,410 --> 00:07:15,080
Josuke: By now,
you know my stand

