and fractured energy?

189
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:23,650
Toyohiro: Maybe he did,
maybe he didn’t,

190
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:26,350
but what’s that got to do
with your current predicament?

191
00:07:26,420 --> 00:07:28,220
