to the slashed steel.

198
00:07:39,900 --> 00:07:42,740
Mr. Josuke, I thought
that you were done for,

199
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,640
but you had already won
this battle.

200
00:07:44,710 --> 00:07:46,640
toyohiro:
How’d you pull that off?

201
00:07:46,710 --> 00:07:49,140
josuke: You said
coming up here was a dumb move.

202
00:07:49,210 --> 00:07:50,780
What do you think
of my plan now?

203
00:07:50,850 --> 00:07:53,750
( Toyohiro screams )

204
00:07:58,890 --> 00:08:01,220
Please forgive me.
The whole reason

205
00:08:01,290 --> 00:08:03,220
i started living
in this godforsaken tower

206
00:08:03,290 --> 00:08:05,130
was to get away
from other people.

207
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:07,430
But that cranky, old grand-dude
in the photograph

208
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:09,360
convinced me
to trap a stand user.

209
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:11,070
