210
00:08:11,130 --> 00:08:13,070
he’d make sure
i’d be able to have a life

211
00:08:13,130 --> 00:08:15,540
in the outside world,
so I decided to go for it.

212
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:18,040
Please, go easy on me!
I’m begging you!

213
00:08:18,110 --> 00:08:20,480
If you’d let me go back
inside the safety of my tower,

214
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:24,150
