of my life in peace and quiet.

217
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:34,290
Narrator: New morioh landmark,
the man in the electrical tower.

218
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:36,390
He’s a marvel
of self-sufficiency,

219
00:08:36,460 --> 00:08:38,790
but if you bring him
a bit of salt or snacks,

220
00:08:38,860 --> 00:08:41,060
