to let you take a picture,

221
00:08:41,130 --> 00:08:43,400
but don’t expect him to be
able to muster up the courage

222
00:08:43,460 --> 00:08:45,770
to take off his mask
or divulge his real name.

223
00:08:45,830 --> 00:08:47,230
Josuke: Yeah, that’s fine,

224
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:49,200
but tell us more
about the old guy.

225
00:08:49,270 --> 00:08:50,640
Did he tell you anything else,

226
00:08:50,710 --> 00:08:53,310
like the whereabouts of his son,
yoshikage Kira?

227
00:08:53,370 --> 00:08:54,340
Anything would help us.

228
00:08:54,410 --> 00:08:55,740
( Toyohiro sighs )

229
00:08:55,810 --> 00:08:59,410
well, actually,
he did mention a stand user.

230
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,680
- I think his name was koichi.
- ( Both gasp )

231
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:04,020
josuke: What else
do you know about koichi?!

232
00:09:04,090 --> 00:09:05,550
Toyohiro: Hey,
take it easy, man.

233
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:08,360
