236
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:12,760
so I didn’t think
to ask anything,

237
00:09:12,830 --> 00:09:14,760
and he didn’t elaborate
on who the guy was.

238
00:09:14,830 --> 00:09:17,600
Okuyasu: Get to the point!
What did he say about koichi?

239
00:09:17,670 --> 00:09:20,570
Toyohiro: Well, he told me that
he found a way to eliminate him.

240
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:22,170
( All gasp )

241
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:24,170
Josuke: He said
he got rid of him?!

242
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:26,170
toyohiro: And if
his son’s yoshikage Kira,

