00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,480
then it seems like the old man

244
00:09:27,540 --> 00:09:29,140
might have already
caught up to him.

245
00:09:29,210 --> 00:09:30,380
He said, from now on,

246
00:09:30,450 --> 00:09:32,480
he would do more
than just protect his son.

247
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:34,720
He’d start seeking out
and attacking his enemies.

248
00:09:34,780 --> 00:09:37,350
then he told me that
a recently created stand user

249
00:09:37,420 --> 00:09:39,790
eliminated a user named koichi
just this morning.

250
00:09:39,850 --> 00:09:41,790
But that’s all. I swear.

251
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:43,490
( All gasp )

252
00:09:44,830 --> 00:09:48,130
Kinoto: Hmm,
and this would be--

253
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:50,530
( yelps ) Goodness!
Look at this door.

254
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:53,170
this will be
about 800,000 yen by itself!

255
00:09:53,230 --> 00:09:56,700
And these designs are from
the victorian or edwardian era,

256
00:09:56,770 --> 00:09:58,740
and they even use
English-made materials.

257
00:09:58,810 --> 00:10:01,280
This is going to be a doozy.

258
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:04,150
Rohan: So he doesn’t want
anyone looking at his back.

259
00:10:04,210 --> 00:10:06,110
I suppose that could explain

260
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:09,750
his rather odd behavior
when he first arrived.

261
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:11,550
Here you go.

262
00:10:11,620 --> 00:10:12,790
Kinoto: Oh, thank you.

263
00:10:12,850 --> 00:10:14,390
Rohan: Before it gets cold.

264
00:10:14,460 --> 00:10:16,490
( Kinoto laughs )
Oh, i’ll be fine.

265
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:18,260
( Rohan sighs )

266
00:10:20,330 --> 00:10:21,830
♪

267
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,110
( Kira gasps )

268
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:37,710
Now’s not the time.

269
00:10:37,780 --> 00:10:39,880
I must resist.

270
00:10:39,950 --> 00:10:41,820
( Fingernails rustle )

271
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:44,820
♪

272
00:10:50,490 --> 00:10:52,430
Toyohiro: Boy, I really hope

273
00:10:52,490 --> 00:10:54,800
that they find koichi
safe and sound.

274
00:10:54,860 --> 00:10:56,760
Mikitaka: Hmm.

275
00:10:58,800 --> 00:11:00,740
( Okuyasu panting )

276
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:03,610
( Growls )

277
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:07,740
Come on! I can’t find him
at home or at school!

278
00:11:07,810 --> 00:11:09,640
He’s disappeared!

279
00:11:09,710 --> 00:11:12,210
Koichi! Koichi!

280
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:14,820
Where are you, koichi?!

281
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:17,220
I’m not giving up,
you hear me?!

282
00:11:17,290 --> 00:11:21,120
I’m gonna do whatever it takes
to find you, koichi!

283
00:11:21,190 --> 00:11:24,130
Josuke: That’s the long
and the short of it.

284
00:11:24,190 --> 00:11:26,630
I wanna know if you’re
willing to get off your ass

285
00:11:26,690 --> 00:11:28,130
and help me find koichi

286
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:30,870
with your scent-tracking
ability, yuya fungami.

287
00:11:30,930 --> 00:11:32,130
( Yuya growls )

288
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,400
Josuke: If you do,

289
00:11:33,470 --> 00:11:34,900
i’ll get rid of your injuries.

290
00:11:34,970 --> 00:11:36,340
That’s the deal.

291
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:39,240
Yuya: I’ll say it once,
understand?

292
00:11:39,310 --> 00:11:41,280
Don’t you mess with me, josuke!

293
00:11:41,340 --> 00:11:43,340
I don’t play around,
and I won’t forgive you

294
00:11:43,410 --> 00:11:46,450
for attacking me like a savage
and landing me back in this bed!

295
00:11:46,510 --> 00:11:48,780
What makes you think
i, yuya fungami,

296
00:11:48,850 --> 00:11:51,590
would sacrifice my pride
to help you?

297
00:11:51,650 --> 00:11:53,360
Josuke: So you’re
turning me down, huh?

298
00:11:53,420 --> 00:11:55,820
I kinda figured
this’d be a long shot.

299
00:11:55,890 --> 00:11:58,090
Well, see you.
I’m short on time.

300
00:11:58,160 --> 00:11:59,560
Yuya: Wait. Where are you--

301
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:01,760
don’t tell me you’re
gonna leave just like that.

302
00:12:01,830 --> 00:12:03,360
Hey, would you wait a sec?

303
00:12:03,430 --> 00:12:05,500
You haven’t even given me
the chance to bargain!

304
00:12:05,570 --> 00:12:07,600
- Okay, fine! Have it your way!
- Josuke: Hmm?

305
00:12:07,670 --> 00:12:09,670
Yuya: I’ll help you
find your little friend.

306
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:12,310
It’s not like I actually
have a choice in the matter.

307
00:12:12,370 --> 00:12:14,640
I guess I could hold out
for a better bargain,

308
00:12:14,710 --> 00:12:17,350
but then i’d just be stuck
in this dump even longer.

309
00:12:17,410 --> 00:12:19,610
I can’t give my girls the kind
of attention they deserve

310
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:21,480
while i’m like this,
and, for all I know,

311
00:12:21,550 --> 00:12:23,650
they could be on their way
out of my life forever.

312
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,850
This is so horrible, you know?

313
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:29,190
And, besides, the accident
that got me into this whole mess

314
00:12:29,260 --> 00:12:31,830
is my own doing.
I’ve got nothing against you.

315
00:12:31,890 --> 00:12:34,630
Now can you hurry up and
get to the healing already?

316
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:36,460
these injuries
are driving me insane!

317
00:12:36,530 --> 00:12:37,900
Josuke: Quit your complaining.

318
00:12:37,970 --> 00:12:40,340
Shining diamond already
reversed your injuries.

319
00:12:40,400 --> 00:12:41,840
Yuya: Huh?

320
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:44,140
Um...

321
00:12:44,210 --> 00:12:46,240
♪

322
00:12:46,310 --> 00:12:48,910
Mmm.

323
00:12:48,980 --> 00:12:50,850
There’s that gorgeous face.

324
00:12:50,910 --> 00:12:54,480
I’m a stunningly beautiful
creature, aren’t I?

325
00:12:54,550 --> 00:12:56,180
At the very least, it’s like

326
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:58,590
i’m one of michelangelo’s
sculptures come to life.

327
00:12:58,650 --> 00:13:00,290
But now that i’m
getting a better look,

328
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:02,660
I think my eyes
are slightly droopier.

329
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:06,290
Your stand can actually
fix things 100%, right?

330
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,530
josuke:
Count your blessings, douche!

331
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:09,230
Now stop preening in the mirror,

332
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:11,470
and tell me how well
your sense of smell works!

333
00:13:11,530 --> 00:13:13,400
Well, let’s see. I can’t promise

334
00:13:13,470 --> 00:13:16,600
i’d be as good as a trained
hunting dog or anything, but...

335
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:19,110
( Sniffs ) Hmm.

336
00:13:19,170 --> 00:13:22,280
For example, I can tell
that there are three girls

337
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:23,850
walking up the hall right now.

338
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:27,120
It smells like reiko,
akemi, and yoshie.

339
00:13:27,180 --> 00:13:29,420
They’re my fangirls, remember?

340
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:30,750
Based on their scent,

341
00:13:30,820 --> 00:13:33,220
they’re coming back
from the pachinko place.

342
00:13:35,190 --> 00:13:37,730
- Reiko: Yu-babe, what’s up?
- ( All gasp )

343
00:13:37,790 --> 00:13:41,900
Akemi: Yu, baby, you’re out
of that icky hospital bed!

344
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:43,130
Yuya: Yo.

345
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:44,700
Yoshie: Yu, baby, you’re back.

346
00:13:44,770 --> 00:13:46,300
Women: Yu, sweetie!

347
00:13:46,370 --> 00:13:49,200
Yuya: There, there,
everything’s fine, vixens.

348
00:13:49,270 --> 00:13:50,740
- ( Josuke growls )
- ( Women gasp )

349
00:13:50,810 --> 00:13:52,210
Reiko: You’re josuke,
aren’t you?

350
00:13:52,270 --> 00:13:53,540
Akemi: Why the hell
are you here?!

351
00:13:53,610 --> 00:13:55,380
Wanna get skewered
right here and now?

352
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:58,410
yuya: Easy, girls.
I hold no ill will toward him.

353
00:13:58,480 --> 00:14:02,180
More importantly, you gals just
got back from pachinko, yeah?

354
00:14:02,250 --> 00:14:04,620
reiko: Huh?
How in the world did you know?

355
00:14:04,690 --> 00:14:07,620
Yuya: Because all of your skirts
reek of ass sweat.

356
00:14:07,690 --> 00:14:10,360
Why else would you be planting
those supple cheeks

357
00:14:10,430 --> 00:14:12,330
on vinyl chairs for so long?

358
00:14:12,390 --> 00:14:14,700
say, akemi,
you got any chocolate?

359
00:14:14,760 --> 00:14:16,300
You won at pachinko, didn’t you?

360
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:19,230
Akemi: Yeah, I did!
You’re amazing, yu.

361
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:21,200
Here. We brought you a souvenir.

362
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:22,500
Yuya: Now do you see, josuke?

363
00:14:22,570 --> 00:14:24,140
- (Chuckles )
- ( Women giggle )

364
00:14:24,210 --> 00:14:27,110
I am who I am thanks to these
lovely dames in my arms.

365
00:14:27,180 --> 00:14:29,680
Thanks to you, I can hold them
again, so i’ll help you.

366
00:14:29,740 --> 00:14:32,380
Josuke: You said you weren’t
as good as a hunting dog,

367
00:14:32,450 --> 00:14:34,820
but as far as i’m concerned,
you’re even better!

368
00:14:36,350 --> 00:14:37,590
♪

369
00:14:37,650 --> 00:14:39,290
Kinoto: I’m aware
that the upstairs floor

370
00:14:39,350 --> 00:14:41,660
sustained fire damage as well.

371
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:45,290
I’ll perform the estimate,
so please go ahead without me.

372
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:47,430
Rohan: What’s this man doing?

373
00:14:47,500 --> 00:14:49,700
Why’s he so obsessed
with hiding his back?

374
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:51,830
What’ll happen if I look?

375
00:14:51,900 --> 00:14:55,400
( Kinoto grunting )

376
00:14:55,470 --> 00:14:56,440
( Chuckles )

377
00:14:56,500 --> 00:14:58,270
Rohan: I have to see it!

378
00:14:58,340 --> 00:15:01,240
How could I not want to look
after that display?

379
00:15:01,310 --> 00:15:03,440
If I have to trick him,
then so be it.

380
00:15:03,510 --> 00:15:06,480
Ah, how annoying.
It’s so itchy.

381
00:15:06,550 --> 00:15:08,280
If only there was
some way or other

382
00:15:08,350 --> 00:15:09,450
I could reach this itch.

383
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:13,090
I suppose it would be
quite rude of me

384
00:15:13,150 --> 00:15:16,190
to ask a person I just met
to scratch it for me, huh?

385
00:15:16,260 --> 00:15:17,660
( Kinoto groans )

386
00:15:17,730 --> 00:15:20,430
I suppose I don’t mind helping.

387
00:15:21,530 --> 00:15:23,230
♪

388
00:15:28,900 --> 00:15:30,570
Josuke: Right.
This is the place.

389
00:15:30,640 --> 00:15:32,510
We found koichi’s bag
lying right here

390
00:15:32,570 --> 00:15:34,480
in the open with no explanation.

391
00:15:34,540 --> 00:15:37,350
His house is only about
two minutes up the road there.

392
00:15:37,410 --> 00:15:40,680
How did this new stand user
storm koichi and snatch him away

393
00:15:40,750 --> 00:15:43,420
from a busy street
first thing in the morning?

394
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:45,550
Somebody should have seen him.

395
00:15:45,620 --> 00:15:47,660
Yuya: Hmm.

396
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,660
( Sniffing )

397
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:51,860
Hmm.

398
00:15:51,930 --> 00:15:55,430
Josuke, our little deal doesn’t
include me fighting, does it?

399
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:57,100
Because when I
agreed to come here,

400
00:15:57,170 --> 00:15:59,370
I was told that i’d
only be used for tracking.

401
00:15:59,430 --> 00:16:00,640
Josuke: Hmm?

402
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:02,200
Yuya: I won’t feel
comfortable proceeding

403
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:04,570
until you tell me
I won’t be fighting anyone.

404
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:07,610
Josuke: Why bring something
like that up at time like this?

405
00:16:07,680 --> 00:16:10,310
Yuya: Because somebody’s
been tailing you.

406
00:16:10,380 --> 00:16:11,380
Josuke: What?

407
00:16:11,450 --> 00:16:12,810
Yuya: It’s that man over there.

408
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:13,820
( Josuke gasps )

409
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:15,580
♪

410
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:19,450
And that’s not all!

411
00:16:19,520 --> 00:16:21,490
I smell koichi’s scent
on that man!

412
00:16:21,560 --> 00:16:23,190
Of course. He must have
something on him

413
00:16:23,260 --> 00:16:24,590
that belongs to koichi!

414
00:16:26,490 --> 00:16:27,700
Josuke: Are you serious?

415
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:28,730
That’s the guy
we’re looking for?

416
00:16:30,330 --> 00:16:32,430
Hey, you! Come back here!

417
00:16:32,500 --> 00:16:34,400
Tell me what you did
with koichi,

418
00:16:34,470 --> 00:16:36,740
you kidnapping bastard!

419
00:16:36,800 --> 00:16:37,740
( Both gasp )

420
00:16:40,640 --> 00:16:42,380
Jotaro: Mom?

421
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:43,810
( Gasps )

422
00:16:44,910 --> 00:16:47,250
What the hell?!

423
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:48,780
It’s definitely mom.

424
00:16:48,850 --> 00:16:50,620
She’s out cold,
but she’s alive.

425
00:16:50,690 --> 00:16:52,250
Yuya: I was watching from here

426
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:54,320
and still don’t have
a clue what happened.

427
00:16:54,390 --> 00:16:56,290
When did he change
into josuke’s mom?

428
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:58,760
I heard jotaro can stop time
for a couple seconds,

429
00:16:58,830 --> 00:17:01,460
but this is a new level
of timey-wimey bullshit!

430
00:17:01,530 --> 00:17:03,130
And even jotaro wouldn’t be able

431
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:05,630
to quickly swap out one person
with another like that!

432
00:17:05,700 --> 00:17:07,670
josuke: If he had
just come out and hit me,

433
00:17:07,740 --> 00:17:09,400
I would’ve been fine
with knocking him out,

434
00:17:09,470 --> 00:17:11,640
grabbing koichi,
and calling it a day,

435
00:17:11,710 --> 00:17:14,340
but that bastard
went after my mom.

436
00:17:14,410 --> 00:17:16,580
scum like him
needs to be punished!

437
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:19,250
This scheming scumbag
is going down!

438
00:17:19,310 --> 00:17:21,680
hey, yuya! Where’s
that piece of shit hiding?!

439
00:17:21,750 --> 00:17:23,420
I’ll make him pay
for what he’s done!

440
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,820
Yuya: How the hell would I know?

441
00:17:24,890 --> 00:17:27,090
You were touching the guy
and managed to lose him!

442
00:17:27,160 --> 00:17:30,190
wait a sec.
He’s still here, josuke!

443
00:17:30,260 --> 00:17:33,390
i’m still picking up
a trace of his scent nearby!

444
00:17:35,460 --> 00:17:38,400
Man: Hmm. Yuya fungami, eh?

445
00:17:38,470 --> 00:17:41,800
Who knew a simple nose
would be such a nuisance?

446
00:17:41,870 --> 00:17:45,710
I never dreamed these fools
would sniff me out, as it were.

447
00:17:45,770 --> 00:17:47,710
either way,
releasing josuke’s mother

448
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:49,510
was all part of the plan,

449
00:17:49,580 --> 00:17:52,610
the perfect plan
to observe josuke.

450
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:54,720
Observation. ( Chuckles )

451
00:17:54,780 --> 00:17:58,120
That’s what my stand,
misterioso, does best.

452
00:17:58,190 --> 00:18:02,190
Misterioso meticulously observed
koichi hirose’s movements,

453
00:18:02,260 --> 00:18:04,490
as well as your mother’s.

454
00:18:06,530 --> 00:18:08,230
♪

455
00:18:08,300 --> 00:18:10,770
( Tomoko growls )
That boy really pisses me off.

456
00:18:10,830 --> 00:18:13,370
I’ll just help myself to his!

457
00:18:14,470 --> 00:18:15,470
Eh? Huh?

458
00:18:15,540 --> 00:18:17,670
♪

459
00:18:17,740 --> 00:18:19,270
That josuke!

460
00:18:19,340 --> 00:18:20,780
So he is home, after all.

461
00:18:20,840 --> 00:18:22,540
Show yourself, kid!

462
00:18:23,680 --> 00:18:25,180
Huh?

463
00:18:25,250 --> 00:18:27,350
( Sighs )

464
00:18:27,420 --> 00:18:28,350
Hmm?

465
00:18:30,920 --> 00:18:32,850
( Gasps )

466
00:18:36,860 --> 00:18:39,790
Man: No one in the world
is immune to fear.

467
00:18:39,860 --> 00:18:41,400
( Tomoko gasps )

468
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:43,760
Man: You really shouldn’t
hide the glow of fear

469
00:18:43,830 --> 00:18:46,130
or the tremors of dread.

470
00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:49,200
there’s a kind of fear
that lies deep within the soul.

471
00:18:49,270 --> 00:18:52,240
No matter what you do,
it can never be wiped away,

472
00:18:52,310 --> 00:18:54,210
- not ever.
- Tomoko: Who are you?

473
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:56,310
How did you get into my house?

474
00:18:56,380 --> 00:18:57,810
( Swallows )

475
00:18:57,880 --> 00:19:00,350
Man: According
to my observations,

476
00:19:00,420 --> 00:19:02,350
you tend to swallow your saliva

477
00:19:02,420 --> 00:19:06,050
when gripped with the equalizer
of unyielding fear.

478
00:19:06,120 --> 00:19:09,090
all people exhibit
certain unconscious behaviors

479
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:11,060
when in a state of panic.

480
00:19:11,130 --> 00:19:14,260
Certain terror-induced quirks
come swirling to the surface.

481
00:19:14,330 --> 00:19:16,400
Did you know about yours?

482
00:19:16,460 --> 00:19:18,400
Tomoko: I don’t know
if you’re a robber or what,

483
00:19:18,470 --> 00:19:21,170
but i’m not giving you
any money, so get the hell out!

484
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:23,210
man: Do I look
like a common burglar?

485
00:19:23,270 --> 00:19:24,770
I don’t want your money.
in fact,

486
00:19:24,840 --> 00:19:27,140
it feels like
I should be paying you.

487
00:19:27,210 --> 00:19:28,740
- Tomoko: Huh?
- Man: I’m having

488
00:19:28,810 --> 00:19:31,680
quite the exhilarating
morning, you see.

489
00:19:31,750 --> 00:19:33,550
Being the recipient
of so much attention

490
00:19:33,620 --> 00:19:35,180
is such a lovely treat.

491
00:19:35,250 --> 00:19:37,820
the attention you’re
